{"tid":635550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國會報告點名華為、中興及聯想涉商業間諜活動","createTime":"2018-04-20T08:18:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T11:51:50.000Z","uid":27688,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0c1052c18af937594cc0704a59b97c5da84d7688","tid":635550,"uid":27688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:18:51.000Z","msg":"美國國會委任的「美中經濟與安全審查委員會」發表報告，指中國政府或支持某些企業進行間諜活動，以提高內地企業的競爭力及促進政府利益，並點名華為、中興通訊(<a href=\"http://00763.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00763.HK&d=7BieEHDRrS%2FIJH8FDuFIam6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=43df2d2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00763.HK</a>) 0.000 (0.000%) 及聯想(<a href=\"http://00992.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00992.HK&d=7BieEHDRrS%2FIJH8FDuFIam6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=c1bef02f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00992.HK</a>) -0.130 (-3.308%) 沽空 $7.85百萬; 比率 34.101% 三間內地企業。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n報告提到，有證據證明中國涉及濫用和竊取知識產權，以及由國家主導間諜活動。而與中國有關的惡意行為是針對私營企業及私營政府承包商網絡，以獲取政府敏感信息，及利用聯邦信息系統內之漏洞。此外，中國透過企業併購以購買主要技術知識，及利用內地企業的經濟實力作為國家工具，從而擴大所獲得的經濟優勢。"},{"pid":"f2803e6cc20fa536915898004551111face6df40","tid":635550,"uid":27688,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:19:49.000Z","msg":"打殘中興<br />\n華為又再被提名<br />\n聯想首次被納入射擊範圍<br />\n<br />\n好戲連場"},{"pid":"e5dbd34561a60de70b68baea3dde457215db0fc6","tid":635550,"uid":104699,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:20:50.000Z","msg":"除左恭喜，我都唔知講咩好"},{"pid":"9b07a60280b454fa9349e304cb1a788d2115f9ab","tid":635550,"uid":13205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:24:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa13fe6af561699830e56efe2a866f01e8bdafa0","tid":635550,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5dbd34561a60de70b68baea3dde457215db0fc6","tid":635550,"uid":104699,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:20:50.000Z","msg":"除左恭喜